title: Lunchbox Is Back From Jury Duty! + Phone Screener Abby Auditions For Bobby Fest +  Driver’s License #1's
itunes:title: Lunchbox Is Back From Jury Duty! + Phone Screener Abby Auditions For Bobby Fest +  Driver’s License #1's
description:
We got an update from Lunchbox who had to leave the show MONDAY because of jury duty. Did he get picked? He reveals all the details that he is allowed to share. Phone screener Abby’s dream is to perform at Bobby Fest in her hometown…on her birthday! Bobby gives her a shot to audition for a slot. Everyone shares the songs that was No. 1 when we each got our driver’s licenses..
